Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.64,0:00:18.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:27.13,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:36.47,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.74,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:45.20,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:50.75,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It may have already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.89,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,And just what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:46.64,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's a lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.45,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.77,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's "The Lemon's Scream."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:53.84,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's how you want to draw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:59.05,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,This is how the lemon looks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.89,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,It's not in line with the \Nobjective of the class...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.10,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,But I suppose it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:09.55,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,That said, you should save things \Nlike this for the art club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:12.27,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.02,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,No need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.37,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and finish it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.39,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a fan of Munch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:21.33,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:25.77,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Mochizuki definitely has a \Ndrawing style all his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The lemon is screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:31.31,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, it's the world that's screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:33.84,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,The lemon is covering its ears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:36.03,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,because it's terrified of the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:41.03,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're in the art club, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.13,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.22,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It just started up again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:48.66,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to join \Nany clubs, Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:55.32,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be interested in the art club?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.24,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.01,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.88,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you drawing, Teshigawara?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.25,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,An apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.51,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Apples don't have arms and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.31,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,This is how the apple looks to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:09.95,Default,Mikami,0000,0000,0000,,Be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.43,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}am{\i0} sort of interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:17.32,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think of Ms. Mikami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:21.81,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how to answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:25.42,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.24,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.96,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,She's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't looking at Munch's "The Scream"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.79,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,make you feel scared, or uneasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:50.62,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Uneasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:52.52,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:55.99,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I feel uneasy about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.52,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,The painting draws out that emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.78,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.55,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You like it because it makes you uneasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.70,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't do any good to pretend \Nyou can't see what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:09.54,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.16,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,...it's the same for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.89,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Sakaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.24,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about Ms. Mikami over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:19.37,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:23.50,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, we were talking \Nabout something a little darker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:26.44,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.39,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,...something darker?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.10,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of uneasiness \Nenveloping the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.33,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.25,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you ever felt that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.80,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.07,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Like when I finally made it to the 9th grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:44.99,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,only to end up in the cursed class 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.93,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Sakaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.62,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to tell you \Nsomething since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.58,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's a bad idea now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:02.83,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.62,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:10.77,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.58,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I've gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.39,Default,Teshigawara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sakaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.84,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.56,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.20,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Was it okay to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.18,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:42.46,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't try to stop you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.29,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:45.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.35,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it based on some kind of model?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:50.09,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you make it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.27,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Both, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.35,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,At the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:01.14,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give her enormous wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.78,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is she an angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.95,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:09.70,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing out \Nin the rain yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.81,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:17.47,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite is the cold rain \Nthat falls in midwinter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.46,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,just before it turns into snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.50,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with your left eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You've been wearing that eyepatch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.28,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,since I met you in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.42,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:32.05,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to tell me, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.63,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.72,Default,Chibiki,0000,0000,0000,,You should head back to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.27,Default,Chibiki,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.92,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakakibara, from the 9th grade's class 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:47.07,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I just transferred here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.23,Default,Chibiki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chibiki, the librarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:52.85,Default,Chibiki,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to come \Nhere anytime you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.74,Default,Chibiki,0000,0000,0000,,but you should get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.55,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:17.35,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:18.68,Default,Bird,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.22,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Chibiki, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:23.13,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that was his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.12,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,He acted like he was the master of that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:29.46,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,He does give that impression, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.29,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,The master of the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:36.26,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Antisocial, always dressed in black,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.98,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,he gave almost all of us girls the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.58,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.59,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.30,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.08,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Has the auxiliary library \Nalways been in that room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.54,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.87,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,But it only became the auxiliary library
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:54.27,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,after the new building was finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.10,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Kouichi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.95,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,are you going to join a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.80,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:06.70,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.16,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was invited to join the art club today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:11.61,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like art?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.64,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,It interests me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:17.25,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very good at drawing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:18.90,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:23.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I've never told anyone \Nthis before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:26.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I'd like to go \Nto a fine arts school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.50,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's news to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to study carving and sculpting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.36,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Does that sound crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.72,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, your father \Nwill undoubtedly oppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:44.01,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Second, even if you graduate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.28,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,you won't have any marketable skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.13,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Talent is a key factor, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.49,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,but without some luck on your \Nside, you're likely to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:56.75,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's what you want \Nto do, you might as well try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.32,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,It's just pathetic to give up on something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.21,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,before you even give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.99,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.69,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:10.96,Default,Reiko,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you look good or \Npathetic in your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:14.01,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.41,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.78,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We're swamped during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:59.25,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for me to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.37,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:04.39,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:10.10,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you reading these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.42,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,The author you recommended to me, John Saul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:20.65,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could get my coworkers \Nto read his stuff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:24.31,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not what you \Ncame to talk about, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.24,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.37,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:33.25,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did a girl die at this hospital last Monday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.30,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Last Monday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:38.70,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,You were still here then, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:39.67,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.91,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened that made me wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.22,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling you're asking for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:53.69,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,There were no deaths among the \Npatients I was in charge of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.68,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Changing the subject, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:57.41,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:12:00.15,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,wearing a school uniform in any \Nof the wards that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.57,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,A girl, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:05.07,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,She had a dark blue blazer, short hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:08.70,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,and an eyepatch over her left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:10.85,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,An eyepatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.54,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,So, an ophthalmology patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.54,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.77,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,You saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.33,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.02,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,But a girl who died...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.39,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,There might have been one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.93,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.58,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:35.01,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was a girl, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:39.49,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I heard someone say a young patient died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.07,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What was the patient's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.05,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to find out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:47.18,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.53,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I could ask around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:54.00,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,If I dig anything up, I'll call your cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:59.74,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I know I've already asked, \Nbut are you sure it's okay for you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.74,0:13:02.92,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just say you were \Nconcerned for a classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.44,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have a good \Nreason to want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:09.81,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,But in return, you'll have to \Ntell me that reason sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.58,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, mister horror lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:20.27,Default,Kubodera,0000,0000,0000,,As you all know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.89,Default,Kubodera,0000,0000,0000,,haiku is a type of fixed form poetry \Nconsisting of seventeen syllables,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:26.72,Default,Kubodera,0000,0000,0000,,divided into lines of five, seven, and five.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:29.78,Default,Kubodera,0000,0000,0000,,However, the term "haiku" \Nitself is relatively new.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.37,Default,Kubodera,0000,0000,0000,,The name was coined approximately
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:36.02,Default,Kubodera,0000,0000,0000,,one hundred years ago by \Na man named Shiki Masaoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:39.79,Default,Kubodera,0000,0000,0000,,Prior to then, the poems \Nwere called "haikai."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:45.63,Default,Kubodera,0000,0000,0000,,There are three important \Nrules for composing haiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.35,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:55.70,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Are you heading home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:57.23,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.35,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:14.84,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,So you were born at Yomiyama Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.81,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,My family moved to Tokyo \Nshortly after, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:19.82,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And you lived in Tokyo from then on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:20.79,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.65,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever come back to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.61,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,My mom died right after she had me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:27.42,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,so not often.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:29.56,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.71,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.19,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I get this nagging feeling \NI've met you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.32,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.27,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're mistaking me for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:41.10,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of why I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.58,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,So annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.34,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.23,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.91,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.88,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm annoyed that I can't remember it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:55.31,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.68,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is part of being \Nthe head of countermeasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:59.25,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:03.38,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly does the \Nhead of countermeasures do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:08.66,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,In simple terms, I'm in \Ncharge of devising and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:12.01,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,executing countermeasures \Nto protect the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.06,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the class?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.25,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Devising? Executing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:19.12,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make sure you understand \Nthe situation class 3 is in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:20.70,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,and the rules we must follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.07,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Akazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:22.69,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.98,Default,Mochizuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.63,Default,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:34.53,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.82,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:39.06,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I miss one day of school, \Nand this is what happens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.31,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.46,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Misakichou 3-3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:08.38,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The Hollow Blue Eyes of Yomi at Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:07.50,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,"The Hollow Blue Eyes of Yomi at Twilight."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.50,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:21.35,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Feel free to drop in. \N-Studio M
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:42.62,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.89,0:17:43.99,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:45.84,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Mizuno?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.39,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,About what we discussed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.38,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:54.05,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,They said it was a junior high school girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:58.22,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she was an only daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.30,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,so her parents were devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.03,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,And her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.40,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,What was the girl's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.72,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:09.81,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:13.32,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I think her name was Misaki, or Masaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.85,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.41,Default,Mizuno,0000,0000,0000,,I only heard it secondhand, \Nso I don't know if it's—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.72,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:48.24,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,My, it's unusual to see a \Nboy your age here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:51.23,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a customer? Or perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.86,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:56.49,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this is a shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.08,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a junior high student?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:00.16,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, at Yomi North.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:05.87,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Admission: 500 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.28,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll give you half price.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.87,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a doll shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:08.24,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,About half and half.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:10.35,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,I also sell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:13.47,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,but not at prices a junior \Nhigh student could afford.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:17.76,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,But, please, take your time looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:21.26,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.85,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,I could put on some tea as well, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:29.04,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but I'll pass on the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:30.17,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.58,Default,Amane,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.26,Default,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}More This Way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.50,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:02.78,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Mei? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:08.24,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you don't dislike this sort of thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:13.30,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.42,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:21.80,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't hiding because \NI wanted to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.42,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,You just happened to come while I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:29.40,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think it looks like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.22,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:33.22,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It does, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:36.15,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But only half.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:39.02,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe less than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:40.93,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:43.98,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't dislike these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:51.29,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you here, Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.97,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:56.17,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I was just walking around, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:59.60,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I don't know this \Ntown all that well yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:03.45,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,and when I stumbled across \Nthis place, I got curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:04.77,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:10.63,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Some people say dolls like \Nthese are creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:14.27,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.69,0:22:15.54,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:21.69,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,These two are my favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:24.62,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Their faces look so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:28.95,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange to me that can they look so calm,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:30.49,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,even though they're attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:34.41,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe that's the reason they're calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:36.24,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:40.13,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It would make more sense for them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:41.72,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,to be calm if they were separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:48.43,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I show you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.72,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:57.56,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,...what's under this eyepatch?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.93,0:24:50.05,Default,Kouichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bone work.
